{"tid":1946807,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"惠譽降英國主權評級至AA-　因疫情增加公共財政壓力","createTime":"2020-03-28T00:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T01:30:20.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eb0860ba8b2ded99540f4d846182f6c717dffc77","tid":1946807,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T00:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1517370_1_L_20200328073345.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1517370_1_L_20200328073345.jpg&h=f101ce49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n評級機構惠譽下調英國主權評級，由AA下調至AA-，展望評級為負面。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽表示，下調評級主要是因為新型冠狀病毒疫情、寬鬆財政立場的影響，英國公共財政狀況大幅削弱。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽又指，圍繞英國與歐盟未來貿易關係的不確定，亦可能限制英國在危機後經濟復蘇的力度。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽的基本預測，預計英國明年的總體赤字將由去年佔GDP的2.1%升至9%，英國整體財政應對方案支出將佔今年GDP的4.4%。"},{"pid":"d911c92f059c4328a2971f4c900f27d142cca959","tid":1946807,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T00:27:24.000Z","msg":"欣賞一下兒登既「英膠」及「崇台狗」如何表現肺炎上腦既青山派LEVEL智力： <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/3xQfRD4Y/1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2F3xQfRD4Y%2F1.jpg&h=79ca5f4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1930886/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1930886/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/LX7BWhrJ/2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FLX7BWhrJ%2F2.jpg&h=0430748a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1931288/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1931288/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"06ff6c7c29d9cb1374306b637e31c48ff8efe0b1","tid":1946807,"uid":225192,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T00:35:25.000Z","msg":"支那送大禮<br />\n用多d華為啦日不落<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkg